    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mangút 是一款没有战斗的单人平台冒险游戏，以叙述的方式揭示了应用程序送货员的日常生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你将扮演一只脾气暴躁、顽固不化、经济拮据的刺猬吉尔。在外卖应用程序 RUN 中，他想方设法赚钱养家，开始了一段充满汗水、挑战和意外转折的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用机械臂在平台上摇摆，敢于做出艰难的决定，在曼古特小山领导一场革命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/b0594dc18c3a010c6b06236a8ab16164.poster.avif?t=1759348315\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/b0594dc18c3a010c6b06236a8ab16164.webm?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/b0594dc18c3a010c6b06236a8ab16164.mp4?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的叙述</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >介绍贫民窟工人面临的困境和挑战；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探讨创业、任人唯贤和革命等主题；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人物形象多样而深刻，世界观截然不同；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有角色都是巴西动物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“焦糖&quot;杂种狗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高速精密平台游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大胆、欢快地在场景中跑、跳、冲；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不损坏货物的情况下尽快交货，以满足客户需求并优化收益；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含二十个关卡，其中有数十个挑战、平台和秘密区域，供您探索并展示您的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/f63d10c06d6c9e39f97f78edf0e7bbc5.poster.avif?t=1759348315\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/f63d10c06d6c9e39f97f78edf0e7bbc5.webm?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/f63d10c06d6c9e39f97f78edf0e7bbc5.mp4?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决策</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对话中的选择会影响吉尔与其他角色的关系，也会影响游戏性；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在关卡中遇到角色：他们可能会提供有趣的支线任务；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天结束时，战略性地使用赚来的钱支付账单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/ed5e6c39fcd8e449cb8f01970320a0f6.poster.avif?t=1759348315\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/ed5e6c39fcd8e449cb8f01970320a0f6.webm?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/ed5e6c39fcd8e449cb8f01970320a0f6.mp4?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古主义的巴西</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吉尔有一个由能量驱动的机械假臂，可以伸展并与环境因素进行创造性的互动；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的人物、场景和配乐都是典型的巴西风格，并融入了蒸汽朋克和赛博朋克元素；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里有四个独特的场景：贫民窟曼古特小山、城市高档区的森林、开放式电视演播室和工作条件不稳定的无人机工厂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有角色都是来自巴西丰富动物群的动物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/b3d766e60fc2e457f821290cfab72485.poster.avif?t=1759348315\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/b3d766e60fc2e457f821290cfab72485.webm?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195840/extras/b3d766e60fc2e457f821290cfab72485.mp4?t=1759348315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
